svg.title: Clouds of the genera Stratocumulus, Stratus, Cumulus and Cumulonimbus: Cumulonimbus capillatus (often with an anvil), with or without cumulonimbus calvus, cumulus, stratocumulus, Stratus or pannus
svg.desc: WMO international weather symbol: Clouds of the genera Stratocumulus, Stratus, Cumulus and Cumulonimbus: Cumulonimbus, the upper part of which is clearly fibrous (cirriform), often in the form of an anvil; either accompanied or not by cumulonimbus without anvil or fibrous upper part, by cumulus, stratocumulus, stratus or pannus
